author: James Rogers
title: UK cell towers torched after bizarre conspiracy theory links 5G to coronavirus pandemic
description: Cell towers in the U.K. have reportedly been set on fire in the wake of a bizarre conspiracy theory that links 5G communications technology to the coronavirus pandemic.
